Package com.fssa.freshnest.model

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.freshnest.model.User
public class User extends Object
The `User` class represents a user within the FreshNest application. It holds information about user registration, login, profile details, and more.
Author:
SusikumarPitchaimuth
